{"tid":307371,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"朱紅的水滴：這是正式錄用的五毛嗎？","createTime":"2017-07-03T10:11:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-12T11:00:47.000Z","uid":4493,"like":39,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"156436b87a74a95384789b90c39b6f875a586d45","tid":307371,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T10:11:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">朱紅姐姐：這是正式錄用的五毛嗎？</span></span><br />\n估唔到支那唔單止火箭失敗，連五毛都失敗過人！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/03/180054_4ffc3e3b7a7e99c6f0ffe915214670c7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F03%2F180054_4ffc3e3b7a7e99c6f0ffe915214670c7.jpg&h=27c1532c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近排新上崗的小同志 <span style=\"color: red;\">西門慶</span><br />\n完全不熟悉網絡長城外面的世界 改圖屈人時竟然忘記抹去Whatsapp右上角的通話圖案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/03/180526_50112559aa12a32e17293ddc6b835e54.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F03%2F180526_50112559aa12a32e17293ddc6b835e54.jpg&h=dc31c326&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">尚未達成任務就觸犯不誠實使用電腦罪 出師未捷身先死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">屈人post</span><br />\n(笑料)Sherlockholmes 原來有份去 愛國遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/306219/page/3?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/306219/page/3?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">被撚狗post</span><br />\n依家d五毛為人抹黑其他會員，竟然偽造whatsapp對話放上連登<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/307076/page/1?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/307076/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中銀61樓：你件垃圾 今晚劏左你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/03/181105_4cf5075a2b323ab9a5a6627103887a55.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F03%2F181105_4cf5075a2b323ab9a5a6627103887a55.jpg&h=c2b2fc43&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ad3de76f25f4ac2b07e9f812de63beb7aae77925","tid":307371,"uid":4493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T10:13:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/03/181339_99bdfc70b11631db01c6dfde694b3618.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F03%2F181339_99bdfc70b11631db01c6dfde694b3618.jpg&h=c6e7947c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/03/181340_99bdfc70b11631db01c6dfde694b3618.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F03%2F181340_99bdfc70b11631db01c6dfde694b3618.jpg&h=d2c60ad9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e1e0799e82e1910b46865750b6f60593bf3e0ee4","tid":307371,"uid":37030,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T10:15:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"222b3c664fc4467d3f5cb13ecf93818b482e6b49","tid":307371,"uid":27151,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T10:18:15.000Z","msg":"五毛狗不誠實使用電腦，我地群組嘅苦主話會考慮組